title: Ranked emblems possibly bugged?
body:
I just noticed that my ranked emblem says "dynamic queue" when I know i haven't duo/trio'd (diamond) for the last 10 games, and i'm pretty sure the majority of my games have been solo before then... i have been playing ranked 5s a lot, so either my memory is really bad (definitely a possibility) or the queue type might be bugged for some reason.

it doesn't really bother me but it might be something to look into.
